{"id": 2031, "genre": 1001, "title": "感情生活中有哪些迹象，会让你认真想要重新评估两人是否合适？", "description": "换句话说，哪些事情会让你冒出“我们可能不合适”的念头？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 3894, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171124143649BN8gqCRwohb1XL0T.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-28T03:00:46Z", "options": [{"id": 251393, "content": "言过其实，言而不实", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1179165}, {"id": 251395, "content": "同一个城市，差不多半年见一次面，总觉得两个人越走越远勒！很好的异性朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163349}, {"id": 251396, "content": "自己难过的时候他不来安慰", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182985}, {"id": 251652, "content": "俩人交流变少", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060924}, {"id": 252420, "content": "想走进对方的内心却发现根本没有入口", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202447}, {"id": 251397, "content": "你告诉我什么叫合适？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197331}, {"id": 251398, "content": "沟通经常不在一个频道上", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197338}, {"id": 251399, "content": "胖了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118081}, {"id": 251400, "content": "嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197343}, {"id": 251401, "content": "鸡同鸭讲，观念不一", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117923}, {"id": 252425, "content": "觉得不能做自己，感觉就是在演戏，而且在一起会觉得很累。目前单身", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202365}, {"id": 251402, "content": "我看好奇心，她看咪蒙。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982279}, {"id": 252426, "content": "开始计较金钱应该就走不下去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1202527}, {"id": 251403, "content": "越来越发现对方的闪光点", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1195889}, {"id": 251915, "content": "互相猜测想法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114139}, {"id": 252172, "content": "所做行为超出自己的价值观。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173829}, {"id": 251405, "content": "出去约会前要做心理建设，聊天像是完成任务，接吻的时候毫无波澜还被他死拽着不肯放", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671570}, {"id": 251406, "content": "没有对象何来……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 251407, "content": "不管做什么，对方总觉得没有按照ta的想法来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197366}, {"id": 251663, "content": "灵魂不契合，互相干涉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1176920}, {"id": 251408, "content": "就是很尬，彼此没有可以分享的任何东西了，不论人事物，还是感情与想法", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 319918}, {"id": 251409, "content": "我差点被车撞到，他没问我怎么样了，反而很嫌弃地自己走开了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1248960}, {"id": 251410, "content": "仿佛找了一个拼床室友，还是自带冷漠脸的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191817}, {"id": 251411, "content": "必须是三观不合", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957389}, {"id": 251412, "content": "喜欢的人却可能不是最适合我的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197253}, {"id": 252180, "content": "生活越来越远……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180053}, {"id": 251669, "content": "说好的是朋友，但是从未有过这么在乎的朋友！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198375}, {"id": 251925, "content": "从未提及过未来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140014}, {"id": 251414, "content": "这条路很长很长很长很长，我只想和你一起走。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181664}, {"id": 251415, "content": "没有女朋友，伤心", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191931}, {"id": 252439, "content": "精神上最根本的需求hit不到", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178178}, {"id": 251416, "content": "一起吃饭不开心 总是逃避感情问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197402}, {"id": 251417, "content": "话不投机半句多", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1181994}, {"id": 251929, "content": "在ta身边睡不着觉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153249}, {"id": 251419, "content": "你和他QQ聊天一般不爱回的，好像自己唱独角戏一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197418}, {"id": 251420, "content": "在一起会很尬很拘束", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197434}, {"id": 251421, "content": "无共同的生活追求和规划", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950354}, {"id": 251422, "content": "争吵的时候，双方都不被理解的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197435}, {"id": 252447, "content": "没有什么共同感兴趣的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062119}, {"id": 253727, "content": "伴侣越来越不相信科学却迷信的时候…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1210033}, {"id": 251424, "content": "命令式口气对我说话，用大大咧咧来为自己口无遮拦当借口", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1185833}, {"id": 251431, "content": "很沉重的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147696}, {"id": 251433, "content": "XXOO 生活不和谐哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197458}, {"id": 253481, "content": "ta关注和转发的意见是自己嗤之以鼻的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898852}, {"id": 252970, "content": "渐渐地有某种神奇的预感，对，就是奇妙的预感，感觉两个人最近感觉不怎么太对，而且还搞不清楚究竟是哪里不对", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1205709}, {"id": 251435, "content": "对我喜欢的，才提就是否定和嫌弃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192935}, {"id": 251436, "content": "没工作还不上进的时候，感觉世界观价值观都不一样了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 207989}, {"id": 251437, "content": "经常说的一个字是“哦”", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197472}, {"id": 251438, "content": "当初拼命找对方，对方却视为小事，后来就考虑对方可能不是你要继续的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1197444}, {"id": 251439, "content": "欺骗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140029}]}